name: Corneo's X-shaped Nipple Pasties TI Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding to add cross-shaped pasties over nipples. Protect modesty!

It isn't completely accurate so may take some gens, and you might want areolae and areloa_slip in the negative prompt if you don't want the areola showing around the X (I did try to train this out as the combination of both ends up too well aligned for my liking). Doesn't mix quite as well with some of my other embeddings either, so perhaps not my usual level of quality.

Example images produced with my 7th Heaven mix available here https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
